Boggle Game
This is a script for a game called "Boggle" that I wrote as an exersice project for the course "Introduction To Computer Science".
Boggle is a word game where players try to find as many words as possible on a 4x4 grid of letters in a limited time.

Features:
4x4 letter grid generated randomly for each game
Interactive graphical user interface (GUI) built with tkinter
Time-limited gameplay where players must form as many words as possible
Real-time scoring based on word length and validity
Restart and quit options for convenience

Technologies Used:
Python
tkinter library (for the GUI)
